{"tid":1413442,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"如何應對車蓄意撞人","createTime":"2019-08-05T09:55:58.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-05T11:24:30.000Z","uid":38928,"like":9,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":22,"replies":[{"pid":"ad0ecb621924343971afafb8bce1a68b1305e2a0","tid":1413442,"uid":38928,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-05T09:55:58.000Z","msg":"如題，已經有幾單<br />\n發夢係源禾路現場有的士狗撞撞入防線有心撞人<br />\n前面嘅手足驚魂未定<br />\n後面好多人唔知發生咩事<br />\n所以截唔切，俾隻賤狗走左<br />\n<br />\n各位一定要打醒十二分精神<br />\n提防周圍嘅人同車<br />\n仲有會唔會有個短號口號<br />\n等附近啲手足聽到可以截住佢"},{"pid":"8085abdcaf512dddd1dc7e78f67540a029819bf4","tid":1413442,"uid":38928,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-05T09:57:19.000Z","msg":"但要注意截住架車係有危險<br />\n佢一退後/向左右亂撞就大獲"},{"pid":"92a9ea6bf6c372705d7ca633a4e7c8813e7979e7","tid":1413442,"uid":282624,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-05T09:57:23.000Z","msg":"最緊要保護自己<br />\n同保護提醒身邊人<br />\n有時間<br />\n拍片記車牌唔少得"},{"pid":"2f526725ef32bc790be464b941eb7f18fcc3a322","tid":1413442,"uid":38928,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-05T09:58:38.000Z","msg":"啱先好多謝位手足<br />\n好快打爆左佢玻璃<br />\n一定要搵隻的士狗出黎"},{"pid":"df7c179aa62fd5d54401a44c6e6b494ad26ea87d","tid":1413442,"uid":38928,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"92a9ea6bf6c372705d7ca633a4e7c8813e7979e7","tid":1413442,"uid":282624,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-05T09:57:23.000Z","msg":"最緊要保護自己<br />\n同保護提醒身邊人<br />\n有時間<br />\n拍片記車牌唔少得"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-05T09:59:27.000Z","msg":"好彩好多手足係上面睇到+影到車牌同事故"},{"pid":"57159566174a2936b59298f93331e35fda307192","tid":1413442,"uid":85118,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-08-05T10:02:55.000Z","msg":"一有機會就dum走條匙<br />\n順便可以老屈個司機阻路<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d121a5b9f76b21646aa8be12e6b1508d2493e985","tid":1413442,"uid":38928,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-05T10:03:06.0